## Design Prompts for Each Change

---

### 1. Revenue Opportunities Card — AI Optimize Feed

```
Add a new category card to an existing AI optimization feed UI. 
The feed already has categories: "High Impact", "Quick Wins", 
"Low Cost", "Long Term Investment". Add a new category called 
"Revenue Opportunities" with a green dollar-sign icon.

Inside this category show 3 action cards:
- "GRS-certified sourcing unlocks EU green product labelling 
  — est. 8–12% price premium on certified product lines" 
  | Tag: Revenue | Badge: +$240K potential
- "Sustainability score improvement qualifies StyleSphere for 
  HSBC sustainability-linked loan — rate reduction eligible" 
  | Tag: Financing | Badge: -0.3% interest rate
- "3 sustainable fashion procurement programs now accessible 
  based on current transition progress" 
  | Tag: New Markets | Badge: Identified

Each card has two action buttons: "Explore" (outlined) and 
"Connect with RM" (filled red). The card style should match 
the existing feed — white background, subtle border, red accent 
color for HSBC branding, small icon on left, title bold, 
description in gray, tags as small colored chips below.
```

