### 3. SME Quick Setup — Landing Page Pill

```
On an existing landing page that has 3 feature descriptor 
pills in a row below a CTA button. The pills currently read:
- "Fragmented document ingestion"
- "Supplier intelligence engine"  
- "Collaborative transition"

Add a 4th pill: "SME-ready onboarding" with a small 
building/shop icon. Same style as existing pills — 
light gray background, small icon on left, 
short label text, no border.

Below the existing secondary CTA link 
"Access your Supplier Portal →", add a second 
helper link in smaller text:
"Managing under 50 suppliers? Try SME Quick Setup →"
Style: smaller font size than main CTA, gray text, 
red underline on hover, arrow icon on right.
```

