### 4. SME Branch — Workspace Setup Screen

```
On an existing workspace creation form that has fields for 
Company Name, Industry dropdown, Primary Operations, 
and Estimated Supplier Count, add a conditional 
helper tooltip that appears when the supplier count 
field value is below 50.

The tooltip should appear as a soft blue info banner 
directly below the supplier count input field:
- Left: small lightning bolt icon in blue
- Text: "With under 50 suppliers, you qualify for 
  SME Quick Setup — connect via Excel upload or 
  WhatsApp in under 5 minutes."
- Right: a small text link "Use Quick Setup instead →" 
  in blue

Banner style: light blue background (#EFF6FF), 
blue left border accent (3px), rounded corners, 
padding 12px, dismissible with an X on the right.
```

