### 5. Compliance Coverage Row — ESG Assessment

```
Inside an existing ESG Assessment tab for a supplier profile 
that already shows metric rows for: ESG Maturity Score, 
Energy Intensity, Water Usage Score, Carbon Intensity — 
add a new section below these metrics titled 
"Regulatory Compliance Coverage".

Show a 2x3 grid of framework badges:
- ZDHC MRSL → Status: Partial (amber)
- GRS Certified → Status: In Progress (amber)
- EU Taxonomy → Status: Not Mapped (red)
- TCFD → Status: Aligned (green)
- MAS Green → Status: Not Applicable (gray)
- HKMA TCFD → Status: Aligned (green)

Each badge is a pill with:
- Framework name in bold small text on left
- Colored status dot + status label on right
- Light gray background, rounded pill shape
- Tooltip on hover: one line explaining what 
  the framework requires

Section header: "Regulatory Compliance Coverage" 
in same style as other section headers on the page. 
Add a subtext line below the header in gray: 
"Mapped across 6 active reporting frameworks 
relevant to your operating regions."
```

